  We played 
  <% if @i==1 %>rock!
  <% elsif @i==2 %> paper!
  <% else%> scissor!
  <% end %>
</h2>

<h2>
  They played 
  <% if @j==1 %>rock!
  <% elsif @i==2 %> paper!
  <% else%> scissor!
  <% end %>
</h2>

